                            <autogen>--KeyToKey-- KeyCode::H, VK_CONTROL | ModifierFlag::NONE, KeyCode::DELETE</autogen>
                        </item>
                        <item>
                            <name>Control+M to Return</name>
                            <appendix>(Without other modifiers)</appendix>
